			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p class="center"><img src="http://FitBloggin.com/resources/2011/PhotoGroup.jpg" width="500" height="179" /> </p>
<p>It is now officially a FitBloggin&#8217; tradition to squish all the attendees into a group photo. This year we did it after the keynote address on Saturday so we lost quite a few folks but it&#8217;s still a fabulous pic of the troopers. </p>
<p>All the photos from <a href="http://www.carriedphotography.com/">the official FitBloggin&#8217; Photographer, Carrie D</a>, are available on Flickr. We have them separated in sets by day. <span id="more-2004"></span></p>
