<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/47005707@N07/sets/72157626761280108/">Click here for the Day 1 set. </a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/47005707@N07/sets/72157626771266646/"><img src="http://FitBloggin.com/resources/2011/PhotoDay2.jpg" width="500" height="332" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/47005707@N07/sets/72157626771266646/">Click here for the Day 2 set. </a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/47005707@N07/sets/72157626658860115/"><img src="http://FitBloggin.com/resources/2011/PhotoDay3.jpg" width="500" height="266" /></a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/47005707@N07/sets/72157626658860115/">Click here for the Day 3 set. </a></p>
<p>We&#8217;ll be adding a collection soon where all photos can be seen in one spot. We are also considering adding a bunch to the <a href="http://www.facebook.com/FitBloggin">FitBloggin&#8217; Facebook page</a> so you would have the ability to tag yourself. </p>
<p>Other quick notes&#8230;</p>
<ul>
<li>Be sure to leave a link to your <a href="http://fitbloggin.com/2011/05/post-your-fitbloggin11-recaps/">FitBloggin recap posts here</a>, multiple ones are welcome!</li>
<li> Don&#8217;t forget to post shout outs to our fabulous sponsors in posts, tweets or on Facebook. </li>
</ul>
<p>More soon! </p>
